        <!-- Chapter 1 -->
        <h2 id="first-steps">1. First steps after installation</h2>

        <p>
          After installation with the installer (<code>./install.sh</code>), GonoPBX is ready to use.
          The installer shows the admin credentials at the end.
        </p>

        <h3>Login</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Open your browser and go to <code>https://your-server-ip:3000</code></li>
          <li>Log in with username <strong>admin</strong> and the generated password</li>
          <li>After login you land on the <strong>Dashboard</strong></li>
        </ol>

        <h3>Dashboard overview</h3>
        <p>The dashboard shows at a glance:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Asterisk status</strong> – Whether the PBX service is running and which version is installed</li>
          <li><strong>Registered endpoints</strong> – Which phones/softphones are connected</li>
          <li><strong>Active lines</strong> – SIP trunk status (registered/not registered)</li>
          <li><strong>Recent calls</strong> – Latest inbound and outbound calls</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Most important menu items</h3>
        <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:24px 0;">
          <thead>
            <tr style="border-bottom:2px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:left;">
              <th style="padding:12px 16px;color:#4a5568;">Menu</th>
              <th style="padding:12px 16px;color:#4a5568;">Function</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;"><strong>Dashboard</strong></td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Live overview of the system</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;"><strong>DIDs</strong></td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Manage inbound numbers (DIDs) and assignments</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;"><strong>Call Forwarding</strong></td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Configure forwarding per extension</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;"><strong>Voicemail</strong></td>
              <td style="padding:12px 16px;">Listen to and manage voicemail messages</td>
            </tr>
